title: Spittin' Chiclets Episode 282: Featuring Duncan Keith
description:
On Monday’s episode of Spittin’ Chiclets the guys are joined by Duncan Keith. Duncan joins the show once again to talk about the bubble, social media, losing his teeth and a ton more. The guys also talk about the qualifying round and all the hockey that the world has recently been blessed with. The guys also break down the Matthew Tkachuk vs Winnipeg Jets scenario and finish up with a little golf talk.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/schiclets
